- I wish.

96
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:23,519
- No, I'm always on the road.
- Don't tell me.

97
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:27,080
- Hurricane Higgins gets lonely.
- It's not all razzmatazz, Lynn.

98
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:31,479
I can be playing in front of 1,000 people,

99
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:34,119
