watching on the telly.

100
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,679
But I'm a snooker player.

101
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:37,800
In the end, you're always on your own.

102
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,959
Me mates were right.

103
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:45,760
Hurricane Higgins is a right flash bastard.

104
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:51,720
