00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:30,039
Here he is - the man of the moment.

109
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,559
The Hurricane in Romford!

110
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:33,039
Get this man a drink.

111
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:35,959
