00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:15,039
That top cushion has got more
bounce than a pair of Page 3 tits.

145
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:17,080
Thanks for coming, Alex.

146
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:22,199
